title: #636 - Sin Quirin and Cesar Soto
description:
Sin Quirin, a grammy nominated guitar player who plays and writes for "Ministry" and "Three Headed Snake", and Cesar Soto, a guitar player for "Ministry" and "Three Headed Snake," joins Joey Diaz and Lee Syatt LIVE in studio.
